column5: Out pike fishing Monday with sleded, saw a nice beaver house. Stopped casting for a minute to toss a 1" tube on a dropshot rig. Bounce, bounce, hmm yes there is crappies in there!
Nice fish Rich, 3 more for a feed
Great fish Rich, is that a White Crappie?  RJ
Thanks Rob!  Yes it is. I only just started catching black crappies in this pond this year. 90% of what we get in typical spots has been whites. This is my PB white, I think!
Wicked, we don't have em up this way.  RJ
